---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contribute">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Contribute to Nonprofit.ai</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Help us build the world's best collection of nonprofit AI prompts. Contributions are welcome!
      </p>

      <h2>How to Contribute</h2>
      <p>
        Nonprofit.ai is open source and community-driven. The best way to contribute is by submitting a pull request on GitHub.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 1: Fork the Repository</h3>
      <p>
        Visit <a href="https://github.com/earino/nonprofit-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/earino/nonprofit-ai</a> and click "Fork" to create your own copy.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 2: Add Your Prompt</h3>
      <p>
        Create a new markdown file in <code>src/content/prompts/</code> following this structure:
      </p>

      <pre class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto"><code>---
title: "Your Prompt Title"
description: "One-line description"
category: "fundraising" # or communications, programs, events, board, operations
subcategory: "Donor Communications"
tags: ["tag1", "tag2", "tag3"]
role: ["Development Director"] # Who would use this
difficulty: "Beginner" # or Intermediate, Advanced
updated: 2025-11-01
---

## The Prompt

\`\`\`
Your actual prompt text goes here.
Use [BRACKETS] for customizable fields.
\`\`\`

## How to Customize

1. Step-by-step instructions
2. For replacing [BRACKETS]

## Pro Tips

1. Advanced usage tips
2. Best practices

## Related Prompts

- Link to related prompts</code></pre>

      <h3>Step 3: Test Your Prompt</h3>
      <p>
        Before submitting, test your prompt with ChatGPT, Claude, or Gemini to ensure it produces useful outputs.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 4: Submit a Pull Request</h3>
      <p>
        Commit your changes and create a pull request. Include a brief description of your prompt and why it's useful for nonprofits.
      </p>

      <h2>What Makes a Good Prompt?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Nonprofit-specific:</strong> Addresses real nonprofit challenges and contexts</li>
        <li><strong>Tested:</strong> You've tried it and it works well</li>
        <li><strong>Clear:</strong> Easy to understand and use, even for AI beginners</li>
        <li><strong>Specific:</strong> Produces useful, actionable outputs</li>
        <li><strong>Well-documented:</strong> Includes customization instructions and pro tips</li>
        <li><strong>Original:</strong> Your own work, not copied from other sources</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Quality Standards</h2>
      <p>
        All contributed prompts will be reviewed for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Relevance to nonprofit operations</li>
        <li>Quality of outputs (we may test with our validation harness)</li>
        <li>Clarity and usability</li>
        <li>Appropriate difficulty level</li>
        <li>Proper formatting and structure</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Other Ways to Help</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Report issues:</strong> Found a broken link or error? <a href="https://github.com/earino/nonprofit-ai/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open an issue on GitHub</a></li>
        <li><strong>Share feedback:</strong> Tell us which prompts are most useful or what's missing</li>
        <li><strong>Spread the word:</strong> Share Nonprofit.ai with other nonprofit professionals</li>
        <li><strong>Improve documentation:</strong> Help make guides clearer for beginners</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Response Time</h2>
      <p>
        We review pull requests on a volunteer basis and aim to respond within 5-7 business days. Thank you for your patience!
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        Contact Leigh at <a href="mailto:Leigh.Arinodelarubia@gmail.com">Leigh.Arinodelarubia@gmail.com</a> with questions about contributing.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 my-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Ready to Contribute?</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">Visit the GitHub repository to get started:</p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/earino/nonprofit-ai"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          View on GitHub â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
